i thought i was helping somebody else's kid,'' said herbert l. robinson, a state employment specialist. ``i just saw him laying there on the street and people standing around trying to take care of him.''
mark and his 10-year-old sister, joanna, were on their way to school when the accident happened friday, said their mother, janet robinson
