thicke has been criticized by animal-rights groups for his association with the beauty contest, which will award the winner of tuesday's finals a full-length mink coat and a mink jacket
thicke said friday he believes he would be more valuable behind the scenes than on the picket line with protesters who want to educate people about the cruelties they say the fur industry inflicts on animals
last month, tv game-show host bob barker ended his 21-year reign as the miss usa master of ceremonies when he quit to protest the mink giveaway
